{"tid":793060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港獨作家盧斯達，上D100被網民回帶恥笑","createTime":"2018-08-25T05:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T15:31:40.000Z","uid":43785,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5179c0eb892c1e0e77af8d1eed78cf7a728a66d1","tid":793060,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/25/mMwis1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2FmMwis1.png&h=9ac140b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友回帶。佢用左四年走埋去，若D100係賊，咁你又係唔係？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盧斯達（2014）：D100品味惡俗，煽情誇張，為了呃like無所不用其極...D100的專頁經常偷文偷圖偷片，已經臭名遠播...<br />\nD100是一個奉行鴕鳥政策的賊，又是一個典型的香港仔。典型香港仔就是又食又拎，要擺款，但冇料；又要做節婦，又要攞貞節牌坊。<br />\n甚麼講真話，行公義，好憐憫，口號比五毛錢更廉價，盡是鳩噏﹗<br />\n<br />\n有種笨賊叫盧斯達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一向屌開D100及支持&lt;港獨作家盧思達&gt;的&lt;港獨派首席KOL仇思達&gt;表示自己柒左當睇唔到，仍然未作回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2304a3e53299fa93896c0775e72df9f37ac0883d","tid":793060,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"如果梁文道係文妓<br />\n咁盧腎達就係文壇一樓一，400蚊乜都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己咁憎既D100都要上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453ff3ba8082f2bb00d48a7f39dc46e22aac153a","tid":793060,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/25/A1PTgj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2FA1PTgj.png&h=598f11fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友再回帶，提提你腎弟上去做節目的D100同泛民有幾虛偽同賣港。「D100清盤開香檳慶祝」？你走上去乞食乍啩？<br />\n<br />\n盧斯達：狗改不了吃屎，D100改不了抄襲。幾多人鬧、出幾多醜，D100是鐵了心不改作風。<br />\nD100的人...偷人創作還大言炎炎教訓別人；聲聲求「賜教」，裝出個謙謙君子的模樣&mdash;&mdash;惡棍無賴掛著一張君子劍的臉，就是這種。<br />\nD100是盜竊慣犯，是明知故犯，嘴裡說要行公義，背後陰招打壓異己。D100做賊都做出了一套理論，<br />\nD100的問題，只是泛民中人的放大版...泛民中人有六四宗教儀式和在野民主黨派的光環，行事作風其實與D100是一樣的偽君子、真匪氣。<br />\nD100為了呃like無所不用其極，有三十萬個like，好多，那又如何呢，你們永遠不會受人尊重，D100在大家眼中都只是一個像黃世澤的笑話而已。<br />\nD100也是這樣的。為民主，為公義！所以抄你的東西，說得像是關照你、賞識你。抄野，反而是為民主出了一分力。<br />\n到D100有日清盤，我絕對會開香檳慶祝。約埋你地，聽者有份"},{"pid":"993c9ec60c2909cdf62a8eaf62afa7ce417ff314","tid":793060,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"其實盧思達個撚樣不嬲都係咁架喇，<br />\n<br />\n當日選舉同熱普城站台，選時就投比青政，<br />\n寫就屌鳩明報，但就本書就明報出版，<br />\n今日口講支持黃毓民，但就去佢仇家道開咪，<br />\n係講獨心目中，眼裡只有利益，<br />\n<br />\n我相信.....如果鄭大班比錢佢做節目，係佢口中教主都變狗主！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cf6fb9d4dc6359343ec34001324c56c4dc4bc2","tid":793060,"uid":201464,"like":